# Raw GPX tracks — BUILD-TIME INPUT ONLY, never served. Kept out of the repo
# (hard to source / private rides) and outside static/ so adapter-static doesn't
# publish them. The derived profile JSON (src/lib/data/profiles/*.json) IS committed,
# so the site builds without the GPX present. source-manifest.json is kept for traceability.
/gpx-src/*.gpx
!/gpx-src/source-manifest.json
